snippet.title: Amber Heard Taunts Johnny Depp - another audio leaked!
snippet.description:
Think this is the quickest turnover of a video we’ve ever made! But as we explain at the start we think it’s important to get this evidence out there. We have added commentary to give the audio further context, but if you want to know more about the time around the divorce proceedings please follow Incredibly Average on Instagram and YouTube, or follow @thatbrianfella or @queenbpip on twitter. 

Also a huge thanks to Italian Fans of Depp and @mderndarkwizard for letting us use this fully transcribed audio. 

Follow us:
Instagram: @RachaelFerg and @NotRealKev - or @AliceReflected for more Alice Cooper Johnny Depp and Hollywood Vampires content. 
Twitter: @Shellys_Wellie and @NotRealKev 

Please like/ share!
